public static enum HighLevelMonitorConfigurationAPI.MC_POSITION_TYPE extends Enum<HighLevelMonitorConfigurationAPI.MC_POSITION_TYPE>
Specifies whether to get or set the vertical or horizontal position of a monitor's display area.
